            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I have studied here for 4 years now and have yet to come across a school more nurturing and caring than SIS.\nIt gave me the opportunity to take part in several competitions and pick up so many sports, activities and skills that I normally would not have. The teachers have helped me with everything I’ve needed and have made me the person I am today.\nI have watched the school grow and improve so much over the last few years.\nI finished my grade 12 and passed out of school this year…and I think that I can very confidently say that the lessons taught to me here at SIS, academic and otherwise, will help and guide me in everything I go on to do in life.\nForever grateful to the staff, the teachers and the principal here :)",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
