            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Best academics, teachers are very polite and teach with great efforts, they ensure the development of child as per the abilities. School participates in inter school and intra school activities giving students exposure to compete in challenging atmosphere.\nSchool has also started to focus on sports and have started winning laurels. Recently my child participated and was happy on the winning note. Thanks to the new Principal for bringing on the change.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
